<a href="#myModal" role="button" class="btn btn-success" data-toggle="modal">What Do the Colors Mean?</a>
<%= yield %>
<div class="modal hide fade" id="myModal">
  <div class="modal-header">
    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
    <h3 style="color: black;">What Do the Colors Mean?</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-body">
    <p>To Explain the colors here is a rhyeme:</p>
    <blockquote>
      <p>"Weather Beacon <span style='color: red;'>red</span>, warmer weather is ahead.</p>
      <p>Weather Beacon white, colder weather is in sight.</p>
      <p>Weather Beacon <span style='color:green;'>green</span>, no change in temperature foreseen.</p>
      <p>Weather Beacon flashing night or day, precipitation is on the way"</p>
      <p></p>
    </blockquote>
    <p>Thanks to <%= link_to "KCCI, Des Moines", 'http://kcci.com', target: '_blank' %>, for the rhyme.</p>
    <p>Weather Infomation is provided by: <%= link_to "wunderground.com", "http://www.wunderground.com" %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="modal-footer">
    <a href="#"data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true" class="btn btn-primary">Close</a>
  </div>
</div>
